The '''1972 [[Lamar Hunt U.S. Open Cup|National Challenge Cup]]''' was the 59th edition of the United States Soccer Football Association's annual open soccer championship. Teams from the [[North American Soccer League (1968–1984)|North American Soccer League]] declined to participate. [[Elizabeth S.C.]] defeated the San Pedro Yugoslavs in the final game.
