'''Matchedje Nampula''', usually known simply as '''Matchedje Nampula''', is a traditional [[football (soccer)]] club based in [[Nampula]], [[Mozambique]].

==Stadium==
The club plays its home matches at [[Matchedje Arena]], which has a maximum capacity of 10,000 people.<ref name="stadium">
[http://www.worldstadiums.com/africa/countries/mozambique.shtml World Stadiums]</ref>

