{{Speed skating at the 1936 Winter Olympics}}
At the '''[[1936 Winter Olympics]]''', four '''[[speed skating]]''' events were contested. The competitions were held on Tuesday, February 11, 1936, Wednesday, February 12, 1936, Thursday, February 13, 1936, and on Friday, February 14, 1936.

