The '''Syria National Beach Soccer Team''' represents [[Syria]] in international [[beach soccer]] competitions and is controlled by the [[Syrian Football Association]], the governing body for football in the [[Syria]]..

==Current squad==
The following is the squad picked to play at the [[2010 Asian Beach Games]] in December 2010. A number of these players featured at the [[2011 FIFA Beach Soccer World Cup qualification (AFC)|2011 world cup qualifiers]]. 

